### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123456",
  "name": "Test User",
  "role": "ACCOUNTING"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@shopifygenie.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Get Current User (requires token from login)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Accounts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/accounting/accounts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Journal Entries
GET http://localhost:3001/api/accounting/journals
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Dashboard Stats
GET http://localhost:3001/api/reports/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Trial Balance
GET http://localhost:3001/api/reports/trial-balance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Reconciliation Data
GET http://localhost:3001/api/reconciliation
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

